elements.name: Create PO for the IPO process

steps.name: User navigates to Login page
User enters the username and password
User click on the signIn
Click on the Woven Module
Click on Fabric sourcing module
click on Data Entry in fabric sourcing module
click on Generate PO
click on PO Master Sheet
Search with IPO in search keyword textbox
click on generate po icon
Verify the Create PO for IPO screen is displayed or not
Verify the PO details are displaying
Enter Deliver To details and select from the suggestions
Deliver address is displaying after selecting the deliver to details or not
verify the GSTIN number is displaying or not
Enter supplier name and select from the suggestions
verify the supplier address after selecting the supplier
verify the GSTIN number is displaying after selecting the supplier
verify the payment terms are displaying after selecting the supplier
verify that Delivery terms are displaying after selecting the supplier
Enter Lead time in Days
verify the Fabric Details are prepopulating or not
